Label: Inspection Tasks Created
Description: This box is automatically checked when inspection tasks are autocreated and related to this record, and should only appear on the system admin record type/layout.

Label: Reasons for Failure
Description: This fields is used to identify the reasons why a inspection failed. This field must be populated before the status of a Inspection is updated to 'Failed'.

Label: Inspection Notes
Description: This field is used to track notes about the inspection task.

Label: Hide Emergency Map
Description: Determines if the map will be shown on the emergency wizard
